 currently does), but it does not mean that because we have three avenues of dealing damage we are somehow stronger or more versatile.  Wizards may seem singular, but they have ways to deal great damage to any mob - even the lifetap-resisting hyper-resistant mobs we can't touch except with pets - and that is a versatility in and of itself.<br /><br />I would delve further into the matter of balance in terms of these fast-acting new DoTs, but because it seems that they've not yet been finalized I'll give them more time before I render judgment.  <br /><br />But I did want to respond to blanket statements concerning necro versatility.  Now that our ability to solo in the new zones have been taken away, it's more urgent than ever that we realize the limits of our utility abilities and our increasingly one-sided role as damage dealer.<br /></span></font></td>
